name: Colourful Corridor - Limited Edition Print
description:
A kaleidascope of glowing colours captured as the sun was setting on the streets of Cienfuegos, Cuba.

The print is one of 7 designs based on original photographs taken whilst travelling through Central & South America in 2010.
The collection is all about colour and texture, capturing the lands vibrancy and warmth...bringing a little Latin American sunshine into your life...enjoy!

* Digital Print on 250gsm ivory board.
* Image size 28cm x 28cm
* Print size 32cm x 45cm

* Signed & numbered edition of 100


PRINT SOLD WITHOUT MOUNT BOARD 
& FRAME


Original photograph by Bella Brown© 2012
All Rights Reserved
